### Registrar con DNI (Caso Exitoso)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register/dni
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullname": "JUAN RONALD RAMIREZ FERNANDEZ",
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Prueba123",
  "dni": "00415221"
}

###

### Registrar con Carné de Extranjería
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/register/inmigrationcard
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullname": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "Password789",
  "immigration_card": "ABC123456"
}

